Special thanks to nerVo that helped to exist a 3rd version of the plugin.

How to install:

`  symfony plugin:install sfFCKEditorPlugin`

How to use:

`  $this->widgetSchema['my_editor'] = new sfWidgetFormFCKEditor();`

Allow uploads:

In 'js/fckeditor/editor/filemanager/connectors/php/config.php':

`
$Config['Enabled'] = true;

$Config['UserFilesPath'] = '/uploads/assets/' ;

$Config['UserFilesAbsolutePath'] = dirname(__FILE__) . '/../../../../../..' . $Config['UserFilesPath'];
`

FCKeditor Documentation

`You can find the official documentation for FCKeditor online, at
http://docs.fckeditor.net/.`

